Package: waybar-expressvpn-status
Architecture: all
Depends: waybar, nodejs, expressvpn
Recommends: libnotify-bin
Description: Waybar module for ExpressVPN status and control
 This package provides custom Waybar modules to display ExpressVPN
 connection status and toggle the VPN connection with a click.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time VPN status display
  - One-click connect/disconnect
  - Desktop notifications for status changes
  - Customizable icons and styling
